messages.content:
Extract metadata from this book content:

{content}

Return JSON with the following fields: title, author, summary (2-3 sentences), keywords (5-10 relevant terms), genre, target_audience, and estimated_page_count.

Complete the missing LSI fields for this book:

Existing data: {existing_data}

Missing fields: {missing_fields}

Return JSON with completed field values that meet LSI requirements.

Create a compelling book summary for:

Title: {title}
Author: {author}
Content: {content}

Generate a {length} summary that would appeal to potential readers.

Write back cover text for this book:

Title: {title}
Author: {author}
Genre: {genre}
Summary: {summary}

Create compelling back cover text that includes a hook, brief description, and call to action. Keep it under 200 words.

Extract 10-15 relevant keywords and phrases from this content:

{content}

Return JSON with an array of keywords, prioritized by relevance and search potential.

Suggest appropriate BISAC categories for this book:

Title: {title}
Genre: {genre}
Summary: {summary}
Keywords: {keywords}

Return JSON with primary and secondary BISAC codes and their descriptions.

Analyze this content:

{content}

Provide analysis including: reading_level, tone, main_themes, target_audience, content_warnings (if any), and estimated_reading_time.

Recommend pricing for this book:

Genre: {genre}
Page count: {page_count}
Target audience: {target_audience}
Format: {format}
Author status: {author_status}

Provide pricing recommendations with rationale.

Create marketing copy for:

Title: {title}
Author: {author}
Genre: {genre}
Summary: {summary}
Channel: {channel}

Generate {copy_type} copy optimized for {channel}.

Assess the quality of this book data:

{book_data}

Evaluate completeness, consistency, and identify any issues or missing information. Return JSON with assessment results.
